ities to do something intensively collaborative. Your best work comes when you allow other people into it.”</p><p> &#39;I Got Heaven&#39; has been described as a “visceral and stunning album for people who aren&#39;t content with the status quo”, made by people who challenged themselves and got out of their comfort zone, per the press release.</p><p> ”We&#39;re supposed to be living in the freest era ever so what it means to be a young person in this society is the freedom to challenge these systems that have been put on to us,” added Dabice. “It makes sense to ask, what ultimately am I living for? What is it that makes me want to live?” </p><figure id="attachment_3516656" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3516656" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3516656" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Mannequin-Pussy-I-Got-Heaven-Album-Art.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="Mannequin Pussy - &#039;I Got Heaven&#039; Album Art. Credit: PRESS" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Mannequin-Pussy-I-Got-Heaven-Album-Art.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Mannequin-Pussy-I-Got-Heaven-Album-Art.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Mannequin-Pussy-I-Got-Heaven-Album-Art.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Mannequin-Pussy-I-Got-Heaven-Album-Art.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Mannequin-Pussy-I-Got-Heaven-Album-Art.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Mannequin-Pussy-I-Got-Heaven-Album-Art.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Mannequin-Pussy-I-Got-Heaven-Album-Art.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3516656" class="wp-caption